│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ $ bin/opt --passes=print<scalar-evolution>,aa-eval,loop-mssa(simple-loop-unswitch<nontrivial>,licm) -verify-memoryssa -S -aa-pipeline=basic-aa -print-all-alias-modref-info --debug-only=licm,memoryssa        │
